[Release Notes] 
Global DJ & producer Paul van Dyk teams up with top UK club brand Cream 
for this year&#039;s Cream Ibiza album. 

Paul&#039;s relationship with Cream and Ibiza spans more than 10 years and 
this years Cream Ibiza album is the first time Paul has committed to mix 
a Cream album plus his first really heavily TV marketed mix album in the 
UK. 

Reflecting Paul&#039;s legendary DJ sets at Amnesia, Cream&#039;s spiritual Ibiza 
home, this album will see him mix the real sound of Ibiza over two CD&#039;s 
and a mind blowing 49 tracks, taking in genres from minimal and electro 
to house and progressive through to trance and techno but always 
maintaining the Paul van Dyk vibe.
